{"tid":320090,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"11月尾北海道9日求交通行程狠批","createTime":"2017-07-13T09:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T07:08:06.000Z","uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"280ed7c23f65ffafe3e40dc7d68a7138dc5c6e5e","tid":320090,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:33:40.000Z","msg":"day1 中午到新千歲-&gt;登別<br />\nday2 登別-&gt;涵館<br />\nday3 涵館-&gt;二世古<br />\nday4 二世古-&gt;札幌    <br />\n<br />\nday123用JR3日卷 $16500yen x2人<br />\n<br />\nday5 札幌全日<br />\nday6 札幌租車-&gt;旭川-&gt;富良野<br />\nday7 富良野-&gt;札幌<br />\nday8 札幌-&gt; 小樽 -&gt;札幌 還車 <br />\n<br />\nday 678 租車 大慨25000yen<br />\n<br />\nday9 札幌10:00 搭JR去機場<br />\n<br />\nexperienced driver, 純粹想咁多位比下意見我租車係呢幾個地方係咪真係方便過用JR 去玩？ <br />\n定我索性買JR7日卷 剩番一日半再自己發揮<br />\n價錢比較 24000x2 vs 33000+25000<br />\n求達人指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33ef0ce3f33da89c92cd2c18419f16f56a65adb","tid":320090,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"2a6fec87159090a488192ea77eedd60ac206f2cd","tid":320090,"uid":114909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"租車要咁貴?我之前冬天租都只係4萬幾YEN 8日連HEP"},{"pid":"aa8c14363fa82c8c31470c3170aa402f9a81eed6","tid":320090,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>租車要咁貴?我之前冬天租都只係4萬幾YEN 8日連HEP</blockquote><br />\n可能我未格哂價<br />\n<br />\n不過我最想知我租車有冇需要@@"},{"pid":"e4976ed41d7acc9e227f70bcebc69c9bf817d204","tid":320090,"uid":114909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>租車要咁貴?我之前冬天租都只係4萬幾YEN 8日連H