=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，如果同朋友去一定多野夾多野討論好多<br />\n<br />\n好彩我有個傻婆剩係抆衫尾就行<br />\n不過都想盡力plan 個好行程<br />\n<br />\n而加諗住去二世古滑雪，平d<br />\n租車果段經星野村就唔滑，剩係住"},{"pid":"c6a5d00b4b09121aff21b35c1610c53449336447","tid":320090,"uid":5542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:03:47.000Z","msg":"Sky Rent a Car 租車算唔算平?"},{"pid":"3243cb9c338c78c95e78b2bc40c1ef92e79a9754","tid":320090,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sky Rent a Car 租車算唔算平?</blockquote><br />\n最好唔怕煩，幾間都禁下"},{"pid":"974828bcfc403612dfa4f2fa48e565cb8f1a143e","tid":320090,"uid":19371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"我二月剛去完，巴打你知唔知11月尾一定有雪？"},{"pid":"c5a6782f9b8728c9b1bc3623af926d4dd6f06c47","tid":320090,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"你頭三日根本搭唔到16500 Yen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308d51a71a92a11617ecb78b50f4b7b3d27bd309","tid":320090,"uid":100322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:40:46.000Z","msg":"涵館去二世古交通好疏<br />\n自己check下<br />\n時間有幾多限制<br />\n留一晚有d趕"},{"pid":"71e551f7b4ace49d3297924a1d0aa3ce0e6f58b9","tid":320090,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"全程drive la"}]}